{"tid":910040,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友星期五生日 晚飯食咩好","createTime":"2018-11-21T00:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T12:45:20.000Z","uid":60171,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1e835d5db9852a415281d937031e846288432095","tid":910040,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T00:56:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的，唔係山窮水盡我都唔想喺度問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我呢位老友真係好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢對食有份on9嘅固執，好難服侍，成個女人咁，唔食呢樣唔食嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仆街好似湊仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話就話唔食海鮮，但又會食魚生壽司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩鳩我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住生日又話唔想留喺佢屋企食喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人數目前有7人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有無咩諗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為食完飯大家都會去佢屋企，所以地點揀左元朗區<br />\n唔要b仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab98ee0d7b9ca40bc0d4df46e50322691f929a0","tid":910040,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:07:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b798d1fee2fa5832d9271f54ec2267a8a26fc48f",